    <title>Installation of libzeitgeist</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>libzeitgeist</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
